1
00:00:01,639 --> 00:00:04,796
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Raluva told us there
was once a Filolial Queen</b></Default>

2
00:00:04,820 --> 00:00:06,365
<Default><b>one that
looked like Filo</b></Default>

3
00:00:06,389 --> 00:00:08,665
<Default><b>that was worshipped
throughout Q'ten Lo.</b></Default>

4
00:00:08,689 --> 00:00:10,866
<Default><b>Because of that</b></Default>

5
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:13,735
<Default><b>as we began our march
to the old capital.</b></Default>

6
00:00:13,759 --> 00:00:15,966
<Default><b>The effect
was incredible.</b></Default>

7
00:00:15,990 --> 00:00:18,515
<Default><b>We were welcomed
in every town we passed.</b></Default>

8
00:00:18,539 --> 00:00:21,386
<Default><b>Not to mention we were able
to garner their support</b></Default>

9
00:00:21,410 --> 00:00:23,730
<Default><b>without having to
raise a sword.</b></Default>

10
00:00:29,510 --> 00:00:31,565
<Default><b>I can't believe she's having
such an incredible effect</b></Default>

11
00:00:31,589 --> 00:00:33,555
<Default><b>- on people.
- [laughter]</b></Default>

12
00:00:33,579 --> 00:00:36,036
<Default><b>Funny you say that, 'cause
the same could be said</b></Default>

13
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:37,426
<Default><b>for you, Raphtalia.</b></Default>

14
00:00:37,450 --> 00:00:38,427
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

15
00:00:38,451 --> 00:00:39,960
<Default><b>He's correct.</b></Default>

16
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:43,595
<Default><b>Seeing you
in their clothes</b></Default>

17
00:00:43,619 --> 00:00:45,595
<Default><b>will cause any
who are unsatisfied</b></Default>

18
00:00:45,619 --> 00:00:48,125
<Default><b>with the current emperor
to join our cause.</b></Default>

19
00:00:48,149 --> 00:00:51,835
<Default><b>It will help us expand
our forces even more.</b></Default>

20
00:00:51,859 --> 00:00:53,566
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

21
00:00:53,590 --> 00:00:56,165
<Default><b>Thanks to you and that
big divine bird of yours</b></Default>

22
00:00:56,189 --> 00:00:58,525
<Default><b>the old capital
is growing near.</b></Default>

23
00:00:58,549 --> 00:01:01,686
<Default><b>For the next few days</b></Default>

24
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:04,846
<Default><b>as we have to wait for the rear
units to catch up to us.</b></Default>

25
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:07,355
<Default><b>I don't love the idea
of stopping our march</b></Default>

26
00:01:07,379 --> 00:01:08,626
<Default><b>but I understand.</b></Default>

27
00:01:08,650 --> 00:01:11,415
<Default><b>Once the old capital
is in our control</b></Default>

28
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:13,176
<Default><b>the imperial
succession ceremony</b></Default>

29
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,080
<Default><b>will be at the
Holy Grounds.</b></Default>

30
00:01:15,650 --> 00:01:16,965
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

31
00:01:16,989 --> 00:01:19,846
<Default><b>It'll give you
the emperor's powers.</b></Default>

32
00:01:19,870 --> 00:01:22,846
<Default><b>But in no way does it mean you
have to become the emperor.</b></Default>

33
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:26,406
<Default><b>So try not to let it
worry you too much.</b></Default>

34
00:01:26,430 --> 00:01:28,396
<Default><b>I'll try my best.</b></Default>

35
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:31,870
<Default><b>[rustling]</b></Default>

36
00:01:32,870 --> 00:01:34,090
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

37
00:01:35,849 --> 00:01:36,995
<Default><b>Oh, dear.</b></Default>

38
00:01:37,019 --> 00:01:38,105
<Default><b>This way?</b></Default>

39
00:01:38,129 --> 00:01:39,195
<Default><b>That way?</b></Default>

40
00:01:39,219 --> 00:01:40,579
<Default><b>Where are they?</b></Default>

41
00:01:41,790 --> 00:01:44,055
<Default><b>I heard they were
somewhere around here.</b></Default>

42
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:45,536
<Default><b>But where?</b></Default>

43
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,537
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

44
00:01:46,561 --> 00:01:47,841
<Default><b>Is that them?</b></Default>

45
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:50,566
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

46
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:51,567
<Default><b>That way!</b></Default>

47
00:01:51,591 --> 00:01:55,006
<Default><b>Hmm, hmm, hmm, hmm.</b></Default>

48
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:58,665
<Default><b>[theme music]</b></Default>

49
00:01:58,689 --> 00:02:01,866
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

50
00:02:01,890 --> 00:02:04,126
<Default><b>♪ No need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

51
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,626
<Default><b>♪ Nothing standing
in our way ♪</b></Default>

52
00:02:05,650 --> 00:02:06,745
<Default><b>♪ Fight right now ♪</b></Default>

53
00:02:06,769 --> 00:02:08,925
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

54
00:02:08,949 --> 00:02:12,466
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

55
00:02:12,490 --> 00:02:15,086
<Default><b>♪ The reason that I choose
to fly when I travel ♪</b></Default>

56
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:18,656
<Default><b>♪ Prove that I exhale ♪</b></Default>

57
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:20,526
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

58
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:21,906
<Default><b>♪ Leaving no regrets ♪</b></Default>

59
00:02:21,930 --> 00:02:24,485
<Default><b>♪ It seems like
a never-ending genocide ♪</b></Default>

60
00:02:24,509 --> 00:02:25,786
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

61
00:02:25,810 --> 00:02:30,415
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

62
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:33,445
<Default><b>♪ Let the pieces
of your story grow ♪</b></Default>

63
00:02:33,469 --> 00:02:34,895
<Default><b>♪ Don't let it go ♪</b></Default>

64
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,325
<Default><b>♪ Don't let it go ♪</b></Default>

65
00:02:36,349 --> 00:02:39,295
<Default><b>♪ Cause you don't want
me nor anyone else ♪</b></Default>

66
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:43,126
<Default><b>♪ No limit to
where we go ♪</b></Default>

67
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:46,735
<Default><b>♪ I will rock the show ♪</b></Default>

68
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:49,096
<Default><b>♪ No matter
what comes next ♪</b></Default>

69
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:52,605
<Default><b>♪ 'Cause every time again
I stand my ground ♪</b></Default>

70
00:02:52,629 --> 00:02:54,836
<Default><b>♪ We never losing prey ♪</b></Default>

71
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:58,325
<Default><b>♪ Now nobody can
stop us no way ♪</b></Default>

72
00:02:58,349 --> 00:03:00,436
<Default><b>♪ We break
through every time ♪</b></Default>

73
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:02,015
<Default><b>♪ It was just pushing
through the frame ♪</b></Default>

74
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:04,265
<Default><b>♪ To something that
we can stake out ♪</b></Default>

75
00:03:04,289 --> 00:03:07,506
<Default><b>♪ Even if there's no end
to this road ♪</b></Default>

76
00:03:07,530 --> 00:03:11,235
<Default><b>♪ We protect
our resolution ♪</b></Default>

77
00:03:11,259 --> 00:03:12,496
<Default><b>♪ Yeah ♪</b></Default>

78
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:14,885
<Default><b>♪ Hey, no need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

79
00:03:14,909 --> 00:03:16,295
<Default><b>♪ Nothing standing
in our way ♪</b></Default>

80
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:18,406
<Default><b>♪ Fight right now ♪</b></Default>

81
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:20,855
<Default><b>♪ Hey, no need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

82
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:21,856
<Default><b>♪ Don't look back ♪</b></Default>

83
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,205
<Default><b>♪ No space for it ♪</b></Default>

84
00:03:23,229 --> 00:03:24,976
<Default><b>♪ Go now ♪</b></Default>

85
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,840
<Default><b>EPISODE 9: ZODIA</b></Default>

86
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:30,955
<Default><b>So I take it our enemies
still don't want</b></Default>

87
00:03:30,979 --> 00:03:32,355
<Default><b>a ceasefire with us?</b></Default>

88
00:03:32,379 --> 00:03:36,096
<Default><b>The imperial advisor
would never allow that.</b></Default>

89
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,635
<Default><b>I've been hearing reports
that the government's army</b></Default>

90
00:03:38,659 --> 00:03:41,406
<Default><b>is gathering
at the old capital.</b></Default>

91
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:44,466
<Default><b>Sounds like they're ready
to go to war against us.</b></Default>

92
00:03:44,490 --> 00:03:46,346
<Default><b>The emperor's
personal troops are led</b></Default>

93
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:47,966
<Default><b>by the Water Dragon Miko</b></Default>

94
00:03:47,990 --> 00:03:49,836
<Default><b>who has already entered
the capital.</b></Default>

95
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:51,836
<Default><b>What information
do we have on them?</b></Default>

96
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:55,955
<Default><b>Unfortunately, we've sent
many spies to find out.</b></Default>

97
00:03:55,979 --> 00:03:58,376
<Default><b>But not a single one
has returned.</b></Default>

98
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,885
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

99
00:03:59,909 --> 00:04:02,846
<Default><b>I really wish
I could help</b></Default>

100
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,735
<Default><b>has happened
here since I left.</b></Default>

101
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:08,235
<Default><b>I'm sure it's someone
from my clan, but...</b></Default>

102
00:04:08,259 --> 00:04:10,406
<Default><b>So even if we get
to the old capital</b></Default>

103
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:13,126
<Default><b>we'll still end up having
to fight, won't we?</b></Default>

104
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:15,175
<Default><b>Stay sharp out
there, everyone.</b></Default>

105
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,176
<Default><b>[ALL] Right.</b></Default>

106
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:18,675
<Default><b>[suspenseful music]</b></Default>

107
00:04:18,699 --> 00:04:20,466
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

108
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:21,846
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

109
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,865
<Default><b>I hope you're hungry</b></Default>

110
00:04:23,889 --> 00:04:25,726
<Default><b>food's ready, Master.</b></Default>

111
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:27,065
<Default><b>Sorry.</b></Default>

112
00:04:27,089 --> 00:04:28,826
<Default><b>I'm actually going out
to check the forge.</b></Default>

113
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:31,156
<Default><b>You guys go ahead
and eat without me.</b></Default>

114
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:34,555
<Default><b>Raphtalia and Filo, there's
another parade tomorrow.</b></Default>

115
00:04:34,579 --> 00:04:36,026
<Default><b>Try and get some rest.</b></Default>

116
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:39,855
<Default><b>Atla and Fohl, I want you
training after dinner.</b></Default>

117
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:41,906
<Default><b>Please be careful</b></Default>

118
00:04:41,930 --> 00:04:43,815
<Default><b>You really ought
to just let me accompany you</b></Default>

119
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:45,086
<Default><b>as your bodyguard.</b></Default>

120
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:47,175
<Default><b>It's too dangerous
to go alone.</b></Default>

121
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:49,355
<Default><b>I'm fine. Thanks.</b></Default>

122
00:04:49,379 --> 00:04:51,105
<Default><b>Just to be safe</b></Default>

123
00:04:51,129 --> 00:04:53,516
<Default><b>let us protect you while
you're on your way there.</b></Default>

124
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:56,315
<Default><b>After that, I promise
we'll do whatever you want.</b></Default>

125
00:04:56,339 --> 00:04:57,995
<Default><b>That's kind of you</b></Default>

126
00:04:58,019 --> 00:05:00,276
<Default><b>I told you two
to train together.</b></Default>

127
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:03,430
<Default><b>Stop spoiling Atla
and do what's best for her.</b></Default>

128
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,995
<Default><b>I will be the protection
you require.</b></Default>

129
00:05:07,019 --> 00:05:09,526
<Default><b>She says nobody
gave her orders.</b></Default>

130
00:05:09,550 --> 00:05:11,995
<Default><b>So she's protecting you
of her own free will.</b></Default>

131
00:05:12,019 --> 00:05:13,019
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

132
00:05:14,939 --> 00:05:16,586
<Default><b>I'm leaving
you in charge.</b></Default>

133
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:17,625
<Default><b>OK.</b></Default>

134
00:05:17,649 --> 00:05:18,776
<Default><b>Good luck.</b></Default>

135
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,406
<Default><b>And take good care
of him, Sane.</b></Default>

136
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:21,685
<Default><b>Well, I hope
you're happy.</b></Default>

137
00:05:21,709 --> 00:05:23,346
<Default><b>I lost my job
because of you, brother.</b></Default>

138
00:05:23,370 --> 00:05:24,347
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

139
00:05:24,371 --> 00:05:25,875
<Default><b>I was doing it for you.</b></Default>

140
00:05:25,899 --> 00:05:27,065
<Default><b>I didn't ask you to.</b></Default>

141
00:05:27,089 --> 00:05:28,396
<Default><b>You should have
stayed out of it.</b></Default>

142
00:05:28,420 --> 00:05:29,446
<Default><b>[FOHL] Stayed out?</b></Default>

143
00:05:29,470 --> 00:05:32,339
<Default><b>[crickets chirping]</b></Default>

144
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:37,660
<Default><b>[footsteps, clash]</b></Default>

145
00:05:39,540 --> 00:05:40,625
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Whoa!</b></Default>

146
00:05:40,649 --> 00:05:41,626
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

147
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:43,065
<Default><b>I'm so sorry about that.</b></Default>

148
00:05:43,089 --> 00:05:44,569
<Default><b>No, it was my bad.</b></Default>

149
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:48,036
<Default><b>Is there
something wrong?</b></Default>

150
00:05:48,060 --> 00:05:49,675
<Default><b>I'm fine.
Are you OK?</b></Default>

151
00:05:49,699 --> 00:05:50,716
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

152
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:52,745
<Default><b>But maybe you
can help me.</b></Default>

153
00:05:52,769 --> 00:05:55,665
<Default><b>Do you know where I can
find the main street?</b></Default>

154
00:05:55,689 --> 00:05:56,886
<Default><b>The main street, huh?</b></Default>

155
00:05:56,910 --> 00:05:58,536
<Default><b>I know.</b></Default>

156
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,495
<Default><b>It's right down
that road over there.</b></Default>

157
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,536
<Default><b>Whoa!</b></Default>

158
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,696
<Default><b>A talking
stuffed animal.</b></Default>

159
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,315
<Default><b>How cute.</b></Default>

160
00:06:05,339 --> 00:06:07,125
<Default><b>Oh, you're
flattering me.</b></Default>

161
00:06:07,149 --> 00:06:09,495
<Default><b>Well, don't let us keep you
from your destination.</b></Default>

162
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:11,505
<Default><b>Oh, that's what
I was doing.</b></Default>

163
00:06:11,529 --> 00:06:13,425
<Default><b>It's just over this way</b></Default>

164
00:06:13,449 --> 00:06:14,605
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] No!</b></Default>

165
00:06:14,629 --> 00:06:15,606
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

166
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:17,146
<Default><b>It's that way.</b></Default>

167
00:06:17,170 --> 00:06:18,675
<Default><b>[laughs] I remember now.</b></Default>

168
00:06:18,699 --> 00:06:20,519
<Default><b>Thank you so very much.</b></Default>

169
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:26,045
<Default><b>What was her problem?</b></Default>

170
00:06:26,069 --> 00:06:28,935
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] How's it going?
- [ERHARD] Ah. Hey, kid.</b></Default>

171
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,826
<Default><b>You came at
the perfect time.</b></Default>

172
00:06:30,850 --> 00:06:33,706
<Default><b>Now tell him to take these
damn ropes off of me.</b></Default>

173
00:06:33,730 --> 00:06:35,375
<Default><b>The hell did I just
walk in on?</b></Default>

174
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:37,596
<Default><b>Earlier, he said he
was going to ditch work</b></Default>

175
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:38,636
<Default><b>and go out drinking.</b></Default>

176
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,636
<Default><b>- Hmm?
- Hmm?</b></Default>

177
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:43,045
<Default><b>[struggles]</b></Default>

178
00:06:43,069 --> 00:06:45,045
<Default><b>It's nice to
see you again</b></Default>

179
00:06:45,069 --> 00:06:47,045
<Default><b>You're looking
gorgeous as ever.</b></Default>

180
00:06:47,069 --> 00:06:49,255
<Default><b>In fact, your beauty
is so dazzling</b></Default>

181
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:51,276
<Default><b>I can hardly
see right now.</b></Default>

182
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:53,196
<Default><b>- How about that new sword?
- Yeah.</b></Default>

183
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:55,276
<Default><b>What ended up happening
to that cursed sword</b></Default>

184
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:56,605
<Default><b>we gave you
the other day?</b></Default>

185
00:06:56,629 --> 00:06:57,615
<Default><b>Have you fixed it?</b></Default>

186
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:59,315
<Default><b>Oh, that sword?</b></Default>

187
00:06:59,339 --> 00:07:02,005
<Default><b>For a master blacksmith like
me, that curse isn't nothing.</b></Default>

188
00:07:02,029 --> 00:07:04,755
<Default><b>That said</b></Default>

189
00:07:04,779 --> 00:07:07,865
<Default><b>can only be found at my forge
in the old capital.</b></Default>

190
00:07:07,889 --> 00:07:09,346
<Default><b>I know, young lady.</b></Default>

191
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:11,696
<Default><b>How about you and I go
looking for them together?</b></Default>

192
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,956
<Default><b>With you by my side</b></Default>

193
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:15,925
<Default><b>and be back in here
in no time at all.</b></Default>

194
00:07:15,949 --> 00:07:17,726
<Default><b>There's something
wrong with you.</b></Default>

195
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,906
<Default><b>Sadly, he's not lying
about his forge</b></Default>

196
00:07:19,930 --> 00:07:21,055
<Default><b>being in the
old capital.</b></Default>

197
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:22,555
<Default><b>Oh, great.</b></Default>

198
00:07:22,579 --> 00:07:25,086
<Default><b>So we have to retake
the old capital to reforge it?</b></Default>

199
00:07:25,110 --> 00:07:26,086
<Default><b>[GIRL] Umm...</b></Default>

200
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:27,086
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

201
00:07:27,110 --> 00:07:28,087
<Default><b>Excuse me.</b></Default>

202
00:07:28,111 --> 00:07:30,115
<Default><b>What the...
it's you again.</b></Default>

203
00:07:30,139 --> 00:07:32,485
<Default><b>I'm always getting
lost here. [Laughs]</b></Default>

204
00:07:32,509 --> 00:07:33,709
<Default><b>Young lady!</b></Default>

205
00:07:35,829 --> 00:07:37,396
<Default><b>Who might you be?</b></Default>

206
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:39,216
<Default><b>Oh, um</b></Default>

207
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:41,365
<Default><b>you can call me Zodia.</b></Default>

208
00:07:41,389 --> 00:07:42,675
<Default><b>Zodia?</b></Default>

209
00:07:42,699 --> 00:07:45,295
<Default><b>You have a truly
spectacular name.</b></Default>

210
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,726
<Default><b>And as for me</b></Default>

211
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:49,065
<Default><b>the best one there is.</b></Default>

212
00:07:49,089 --> 00:07:50,745
<Default><b>The name's Muramasa.</b></Default>

213
00:07:50,769 --> 00:07:52,425
<Default><b>[quirky music]</b></Default>

214
00:07:52,449 --> 00:07:54,156
<Default><b>- Oh.
- Huh.</b></Default>

215
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:56,896
<Default><b>I know a place that serves
the most wonderful saké.</b></Default>

216
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:59,055
<Default><b>Why don't you
come try it with me?</b></Default>

217
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:01,446
<Default><b>Hey, get these
ropes off me!</b></Default>

218
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:03,665
<Default><b>[ZODIA] That's very kind</b></Default>

219
00:08:03,689 --> 00:08:06,485
<Default><b>I have to decline as I'm seeing
the parade for the person</b></Default>

220
00:08:06,509 --> 00:08:08,005
<Default><b>who will be the
new emperor.</b></Default>

221
00:08:08,029 --> 00:08:09,706
<Default><b>You're seeing
the parade?</b></Default>

222
00:08:09,730 --> 00:08:11,446
<Default><b>That isn't
until tomorrow.</b></Default>

223
00:08:11,470 --> 00:08:12,795
<Default><b>Oh, dear.</b></Default>

224
00:08:12,819 --> 00:08:14,625
<Default><b>Hey, I'll show you
the way tomorrow.</b></Default>

225
00:08:14,649 --> 00:08:17,136
<Default><b>So tonight, how about
the two of us have some saké</b></Default>

226
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:20,185
<Default><b>and get to know each other
a little better, huh?</b></Default>

227
00:08:20,209 --> 00:08:21,615
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

228
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:23,976
<Default><b>I wouldn't mind going
if you're tagging along.</b></Default>

229
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,055
<Default><b>Sorry, but
I'd rather die.</b></Default>

230
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:27,105
<Default><b>Let's go, Sane.</b></Default>

231
00:08:27,129 --> 00:08:28,466
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

232
00:08:28,490 --> 00:08:31,156
<Default><b>There's no need to be
such a party pooper.</b></Default>

233
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,180
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

234
00:08:34,169 --> 00:08:36,105
<Default><b>Please, I'll fix that
cursed sword for you</b></Default>

235
00:08:36,129 --> 00:08:38,716
<Default><b>and do whatever you want
for the rest of my life.</b></Default>

236
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:40,956
<Default><b>I'm begging you.</b></Default>

237
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:44,145
<Default><b>Look, he's strange</b></Default>

238
00:08:44,169 --> 00:08:46,115
<Default><b>[sighs]
All right. Fine.</b></Default>

239
00:08:46,139 --> 00:08:47,255
<Default><b>I'll go.</b></Default>

240
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:48,559
<Default><b>Hooray, saké!</b></Default>

241
00:08:49,649 --> 00:08:51,960
<Default><b>[MURAMASA] Hooray!</b></Default>

242
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:59,125
<Default><b>[MURAMASA]
Well, folks, here we are.</b></Default>

243
00:08:59,149 --> 00:09:00,956
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
It looks like it's closed.</b></Default>

244
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:04,166
<Default><b>If I'm not mistaken, this
is actually where I'm staying.</b></Default>

245
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:06,265
<Default><b>The second floor
of this building is an inn.</b></Default>

246
00:09:06,289 --> 00:09:07,596
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

247
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:09,625
<Default><b>Then it must have been fate
we came here.</b></Default>

248
00:09:09,649 --> 00:09:11,666
<Default><b>Stop causing
a ruckus out there.</b></Default>

249
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:14,515
<Default><b>The world's too messy
for me to be serving drinks.</b></Default>

250
00:09:14,539 --> 00:09:15,926
<Default><b>Go try somewhere else.</b></Default>

251
00:09:15,950 --> 00:09:17,816
<Default><b>Come on, have a heart.</b></Default>

252
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,446
<Default><b>We won't be long.</b></Default>

253
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:20,446
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

254
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:21,447
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

255
00:09:21,471 --> 00:09:22,605
<Default><b>Welcome back, Miss.</b></Default>

256
00:09:22,629 --> 00:09:23,606
<Default><b>Come in.</b></Default>

257
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,255
<Default><b>Make yourself at home.</b></Default>

258
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:27,255
<Default><b>It's good to be back.</b></Default>

259
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:30,046
<Default><b>I'm coming in
right behind you.</b></Default>

260
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:32,676
<Default><b>Hurry up
before he changes his mind.</b></Default>

261
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:35,296
<Default><b>[gentle music]</b></Default>

262
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,426
<Default><b>[ZODIA] Wow!</b></Default>

263
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:40,385
<Default><b>This meal's amazing.</b></Default>

264
00:09:40,409 --> 00:09:42,135
<Default><b>Whoa, whoa,
whoa, whoa, whoa.</b></Default>

265
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:43,136
<Default><b>For you.</b></Default>

266
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:45,196
<Default><b>Oh, thanks.</b></Default>

267
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:47,096
<Default><b>A toast to our meeting.</b></Default>

268
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,716
<Default><b>Bottoms up.</b></Default>

269
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:51,049
<Default><b>Who made you the leader
of this dinner?</b></Default>

270
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,066
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

271
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:55,255
<Default><b>My gosh.</b></Default>

272
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,275
<Default><b>What are you, crazy?</b></Default>

273
00:09:56,299 --> 00:09:57,546
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

274
00:09:57,570 --> 00:09:59,535
<Default><b>[ZODIA] You sure can
hold your liquor.</b></Default>

275
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:01,769
<Default><b>Incredible.</b></Default>

276
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:06,806
<Default><b>Oh, if it's not too
much trouble, I just...</b></Default>

277
00:10:06,830 --> 00:10:08,586
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Don't even try.</b></Default>

278
00:10:08,610 --> 00:10:10,046
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

279
00:10:10,070 --> 00:10:12,566
<Default><b>[ZODIA] By the way, you
never told me your name.</b></Default>

280
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:13,567
<Default><b>So what is it?</b></Default>

281
00:10:13,591 --> 00:10:15,466
<Default><b>It's Naofumi Iwatani.</b></Default>

282
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:17,696
<Default><b>Great.
I'll call you Naofumi then.</b></Default>

283
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,326
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

284
00:10:19,350 --> 00:10:22,145
<Default><b>So, hey, if you don't mind
me asking, what race are you?</b></Default>

285
00:10:22,169 --> 00:10:23,375
<Default><b>I'm a human.</b></Default>

286
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:25,446
<Default><b>Oh, I'm actually
a Komai.</b></Default>

287
00:10:25,470 --> 00:10:27,865
<Default><b>I didn't know that humans
could drink this much.</b></Default>

288
00:10:27,889 --> 00:10:28,865
<Default><b>How cool.</b></Default>

289
00:10:28,889 --> 00:10:30,409
<Default><b>Well, in that case.</b></Default>

290
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:35,405
<Default><b>Oh, I think it's time
we get a game started.</b></Default>

291
00:10:35,429 --> 00:10:36,985
<Default><b>A game, huh?</b></Default>

292
00:10:37,009 --> 00:10:38,326
<Default><b>Hmm!</b></Default>

293
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:40,476
<Default><b>This one should make
for a memorable night.</b></Default>

294
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,456
<Default><b>This is the
emperor's game.</b></Default>

295
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,316
<Default><b>Masuzu cards!</b></Default>

296
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:45,855
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

297
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:46,905
<Default><b>[MURAMASA]
Masuzu cards?</b></Default>

298
00:10:46,929 --> 00:10:49,375
<Default><b>Sure. Sounds fun.</b></Default>

299
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,625
<Default><b>Hang on.</b></Default>

300
00:10:50,649 --> 00:10:52,296
<Default><b>I never said that
I would be playing.</b></Default>

301
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:55,635
<Default><b>My master says
she can't wait to play.</b></Default>

302
00:10:55,659 --> 00:10:57,495
<Default><b>There. Now let us begin.</b></Default>

303
00:10:57,519 --> 00:11:01,296
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

304
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,015
<Default><b>I guess I win.</b></Default>

305
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:04,686
<Default><b>You're kidding.</b></Default>

306
00:11:04,710 --> 00:11:06,916
<Default><b>But I thought this was your
first time playing this game.</b></Default>

307
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:08,796
<Default><b>I've played something
similar before.</b></Default>

308
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:10,936
<Default><b>Wow, wow.
You're amazing.</b></Default>

309
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,676
<Default><b>Another drink, please.</b></Default>

310
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:14,196
<Default><b>[MURAMASA]
Damn it, I lost again.</b></Default>

311
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:15,405
<Default><b>[ZODIA] No fair.</b></Default>

312
00:11:15,429 --> 00:11:17,275
<Default><b>You're too good
at this, Naofumi.</b></Default>

313
00:11:17,299 --> 00:11:19,066
<Default><b>Oh! That's OK.</b></Default>

314
00:11:19,090 --> 00:11:20,155
<Default><b>I'll win the next one.</b></Default>

315
00:11:20,179 --> 00:11:22,115
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

316
00:11:22,139 --> 00:11:23,775
<Default><b>He's out at last.</b></Default>

317
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:24,850
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

318
00:11:26,759 --> 00:11:29,245
<Default><b>My master says
she's tired too.</b></Default>

319
00:11:29,269 --> 00:11:31,125
<Default><b>We have
an early day tomorrow.</b></Default>

320
00:11:31,149 --> 00:11:32,275
<Default><b>Let's start
heading back.</b></Default>

321
00:11:32,299 --> 00:11:33,276
<Default><b>[ZODIA] Oh!</b></Default>

322
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:34,755
<Default><b>One more game.</b></Default>

323
00:11:34,779 --> 00:11:35,846
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

324
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,255
<Default><b>Let's just play
one more game.</b></Default>

325
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:39,436
<Default><b>You're going to see
the parade, aren't you?</b></Default>

326
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:42,485
<Default><b>If so, you should
get to bed too.</b></Default>

327
00:11:42,509 --> 00:11:45,466
<Default><b>Next time we meet, we're
gonna play Masuzu cards again.</b></Default>

328
00:11:45,490 --> 00:11:46,956
<Default><b>You promise me!</b></Default>

329
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:48,316
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
OK, I promise.</b></Default>

330
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:50,816
<Default><b>Guess we have to drink
to our promise then.</b></Default>

331
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,566
<Default><b>You're still drinking?</b></Default>

332
00:11:52,590 --> 00:11:54,105
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

333
00:11:54,129 --> 00:11:55,129
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

334
00:12:00,049 --> 00:12:02,025
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Don't worry.
I'll get him home.</b></Default>

335
00:12:02,049 --> 00:12:03,546
<Default><b>Get home safe.</b></Default>

336
00:12:03,570 --> 00:12:07,015
<Default><b>I wish you
didn't have to go</b></Default>

337
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:09,846
<Default><b>have just the best time
playing games with you.</b></Default>

338
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:12,056
<Default><b>Probably
because you're drunk.</b></Default>

339
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,520
<Default><b>Oh, that's right.</b></Default>

340
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:16,086
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

341
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:19,255
<Default><b>Here, for you.</b></Default>

342
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:21,186
<Default><b>What is this thing?</b></Default>

343
00:12:21,210 --> 00:12:24,836
<Default><b>A card with my autograph
to celebrate our meeting.</b></Default>

344
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:25,837
<Default><b>Oh, no.</b></Default>

345
00:12:25,861 --> 00:12:27,686
<Default><b>I'm so embarrassed.</b></Default>

346
00:12:27,710 --> 00:12:31,635
<Default><b>Hey, I know it's fast</b></Default>

347
00:12:31,659 --> 00:12:33,019
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

348
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,716
<Default><b>[laughs] Only joking.</b></Default>

349
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:37,005
<Default><b>Gotcha, huh?</b></Default>

350
00:12:37,029 --> 00:12:39,349
<Default><b>I'm not wasting
any more time with this.</b></Default>

351
00:12:40,669 --> 00:12:43,566
<Default><b>[laughs] I hope I see
you again soon, Naofumi.</b></Default>

352
00:12:43,590 --> 00:12:45,566
<Default><b>I'll miss you, OK?</b></Default>

353
00:12:45,590 --> 00:12:47,005
<Default><b>All right. Whatever.</b></Default>

354
00:12:47,029 --> 00:12:48,076
<Default><b>Just go to bed.</b></Default>

355
00:12:48,100 --> 00:12:55,100
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

356
00:12:58,379 --> 00:12:59,926
<Default><b>How funny.</b></Default>

357
00:12:59,950 --> 00:13:01,840
<Default><b>I really meant
what I said.</b></Default>

358
00:13:03,429 --> 00:13:05,086
<Default><b>[cheerful music]</b></Default>

359
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:08,135
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] I'm amazed you
were able to find so much food.</b></Default>

360
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:11,686
<Default><b>Yeah, well, I only got all
of this thanks to the emperor.</b></Default>

361
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:14,826
<Default><b>What exactly
did you do for it?</b></Default>

362
00:13:14,850 --> 00:13:16,169
<Default><b>Here, eat up.</b></Default>

363
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,640
<Default><b>Oh, thank you so much.</b></Default>

364
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,525
<Default><b>Anything I can help with</b></Default>

365
00:13:23,549 --> 00:13:26,086
<Default><b>I think we've got
everything under control.</b></Default>

366
00:13:26,110 --> 00:13:27,946
<Default><b>But can you stop
calling me big sis?</b></Default>

367
00:13:27,970 --> 00:13:28,947
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

368
00:13:28,971 --> 00:13:30,586
<Default><b>Line up over here.</b></Default>

369
00:13:30,610 --> 00:13:32,535
<Default><b>Hey, no
cutting, big guy.</b></Default>

370
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:34,596
<Default><b>Well, I did try.</b></Default>

371
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:35,796
<Default><b>Big sis, huh?</b></Default>

372
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:38,355
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

373
00:13:38,379 --> 00:13:39,666
<Default><b>What did you talk about?</b></Default>

374
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:40,806
<Default><b>[FOHL] Hey,
wait a second!</b></Default>

375
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:42,316
<Default><b>Not much.</b></Default>

376
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:45,100
<Default><b>We just chatted about Atla
for a while, that's all.</b></Default>

377
00:13:46,379 --> 00:13:48,765
<Default><b>[blows landing]</b></Default>

378
00:13:48,789 --> 00:13:49,926
<Default><b>Good grief.</b></Default>

379
00:13:49,950 --> 00:13:52,275
<Default><b>You never stop</b></Default>

380
00:13:52,299 --> 00:13:54,706
<Default><b>Don't you understand
I'm doing it for you, Atla?</b></Default>

381
00:13:54,730 --> 00:13:56,785
<Default><b>Yeah, well</b></Default>

382
00:13:56,809 --> 00:13:58,649
<Default><b>I'd be with
Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

383
00:13:58,990 --> 00:14:00,755
<Default><b>All right. Fine.</b></Default>

384
00:14:00,779 --> 00:14:02,779
<Default><b>I'll go see if
we can slip out.</b></Default>

385
00:14:10,710 --> 00:14:11,687
<Default><b>Perfect.</b></Default>

386
00:14:11,711 --> 00:14:12,745
<Default><b>Fohl!</b></Default>

387
00:14:12,769 --> 00:14:13,769
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

388
00:14:14,769 --> 00:14:16,125
<Default><b>We can go, right?</b></Default>

389
00:14:16,149 --> 00:14:17,936
<Default><b>I'll only be
gone for a bit.</b></Default>

390
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,666
<Default><b>I completed all
of my training.</b></Default>

391
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:21,216
<Default><b>And Atla says
she wants to go...</b></Default>

392
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:24,716
<Default><b>You don't always have
to give in to what she wants.</b></Default>

393
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:26,306
<Default><b>If you're doing
what's best for her</b></Default>

394
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:29,395
<Default><b>then I won't say a word
and I'll let you sneak out.</b></Default>

395
00:14:29,419 --> 00:14:31,976
<Default><b>However, from where
I'm standing</b></Default>

396
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:35,395
<Default><b>it seems like you're only
doing this to spoil her.</b></Default>

397
00:14:35,419 --> 00:14:37,855
<Default><b>No, I just...</b></Default>

398
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:40,706
<Default><b>But seriously</b></Default>

399
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:43,635
<Default><b>something terrible
could end up happening.</b></Default>

400
00:14:43,659 --> 00:14:46,196
<Default><b>If you really want
what's best for her</b></Default>

401
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:48,566
<Default><b>sometimes you have to
put your foot down</b></Default>

402
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:51,446
<Default><b>even if it ends up
hurting her feelings.</b></Default>

403
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:53,326
<Default><b>You want to protect her</b></Default>

404
00:14:53,350 --> 00:14:56,296
<Default><b>the same way
any good older brother would.</b></Default>

405
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,320
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

406
00:14:58,549 --> 00:15:00,645
<Default><b>You're completely
right, big sis.</b></Default>

407
00:15:00,669 --> 00:15:02,686
<Default><b>Huh? Big sis?</b></Default>

408
00:15:02,710 --> 00:15:05,785
<Default><b>I'll stand up for myself
and be the big brother</b></Default>

409
00:15:05,809 --> 00:15:07,476
<Default><b>that she deserves.</b></Default>

410
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:09,666
<Default><b>[laughs] I'll be a great
big brother, the way</b></Default>

411
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:11,255
<Default><b>you're a great
big sister.</b></Default>

412
00:15:11,279 --> 00:15:13,735
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

413
00:15:13,759 --> 00:15:15,515
<Default><b>So that's how it is.</b></Default>

414
00:15:15,539 --> 00:15:18,519
<Default><b>[crowd chatter]</b></Default>

415
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:28,485
<Default><b>But why though?</b></Default>

416
00:15:28,509 --> 00:15:31,210
<Default><b>[ominous stings]</b></Default>

417
00:15:40,370 --> 00:15:41,495
<Default><b>[MAN] Hey, look, look!</b></Default>

418
00:15:41,519 --> 00:15:44,399
<Default><b>[cheering]</b></Default>

419
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:54,346
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

420
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:55,650
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Ah.</b></Default>

421
00:15:56,820 --> 00:15:59,220
<Default><b>Tomorrow we finally enter
the old capital.</b></Default>

422
00:16:02,399 --> 00:16:03,399
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

423
00:16:04,399 --> 00:16:05,376
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

424
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,336
<Default><b>I knew I'd
see you again.</b></Default>

425
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,525
<Default><b>What the?</b></Default>

426
00:16:08,549 --> 00:16:10,155
<Default><b>I hope there's room
for one more.</b></Default>

427
00:16:10,179 --> 00:16:11,615
<Default><b>Wait, stop!</b></Default>

428
00:16:11,639 --> 00:16:12,616
<Default><b>What are you doing?</b></Default>

429
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:14,940
<Default><b>[splash]</b></Default>

430
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,096
<Default><b>Unreal.</b></Default>

431
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,097
<Default><b>Let me guess.</b></Default>

432
00:16:19,121 --> 00:16:20,405
<Default><b>You got lost again, huh?</b></Default>

433
00:16:20,429 --> 00:16:22,216
<Default><b>Well, did you
see the parade?</b></Default>

434
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:25,306
<Default><b>I did, and I got
to see the new emperor.</b></Default>

435
00:16:25,330 --> 00:16:26,985
<Default><b>Did you get
to see her too?</b></Default>

436
00:16:27,009 --> 00:16:29,716
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess
I kind of did.</b></Default>

437
00:16:29,740 --> 00:16:33,346
<Default><b>OK, and
based off of that</b></Default>

438
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:35,250
<Default><b>What's the new
emperor like?</b></Default>

439
00:16:36,779 --> 00:16:40,326
<Default><b>Why do you care so much
about the new emperor anyway?</b></Default>

440
00:16:40,350 --> 00:16:43,716
<Default><b>Well, I think the current
emperor is doing their best.</b></Default>

441
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:49,166
<Default><b>I know Q'ten Lo is in bad shape
and everyone is suffering.</b></Default>

442
00:16:49,190 --> 00:16:52,206
<Default><b>Yeah, well, it's hard
not to blame the emperor.</b></Default>

443
00:16:52,230 --> 00:16:55,416
<Default><b>It feels like my job's been
getting harder and harder</b></Default>

444
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:57,456
<Default><b>and now I have
to do dirty work.</b></Default>

445
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:59,346
<Default><b>That's not what
I ever wanted.</b></Default>

446
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:02,905
<Default><b>Then again, is anybody
excited about dirty work?</b></Default>

447
00:17:02,929 --> 00:17:04,706
<Default><b>Sounds like
interesting work.</b></Default>

448
00:17:04,730 --> 00:17:06,636
<Default><b>Oh, it certainly is.</b></Default>

449
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:08,676
<Default><b>But it's very difficult
right now.</b></Default>

450
00:17:08,700 --> 00:17:10,745
<Default><b>I want everybody
to be satisfied</b></Default>

451
00:17:10,769 --> 00:17:13,235
<Default><b>but it just doesn't
work like that.</b></Default>

452
00:17:13,259 --> 00:17:14,636
<Default><b>I can relate.</b></Default>

453
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:17,575
<Default><b>But at the parade today</b></Default>

454
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:19,795
<Default><b>for the first
time in forever.</b></Default>

455
00:17:19,819 --> 00:17:23,616
<Default><b>And the new emperor was at
the center of their happiness.</b></Default>

456
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:26,456
<Default><b>When I saw
that, I thought</b></Default>

457
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:28,376
<Default><b>some kind of way
to make the whole country</b></Default>

458
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,295
<Default><b>smile that way again.</b></Default>

459
00:17:30,319 --> 00:17:32,745
<Default><b>So I decided
I'm going to find her</b></Default>

460
00:17:32,769 --> 00:17:34,849
<Default><b>and talk to her
to see for myself.</b></Default>

461
00:17:35,549 --> 00:17:38,196
<Default><b>Sorry for rambling
about all of this.</b></Default>

462
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:39,735
<Default><b>It's fine.</b></Default>

463
00:17:39,759 --> 00:17:42,446
<Default><b>Hey, we still have to play
Masuzu cards again, right?</b></Default>

464
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:45,166
<Default><b>You promised we would
next time we met, didn't you?</b></Default>

465
00:17:45,190 --> 00:17:46,906
<Default><b>I guess I did, didn't I?</b></Default>

466
00:17:46,930 --> 00:17:49,186
<Default><b>Let's head back to my inn
and play it there.</b></Default>

467
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:51,045
<Default><b>It'll be more fun
with more people.</b></Default>

468
00:17:51,069 --> 00:17:52,636
<Default><b>Excellent.</b></Default>

469
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:55,176
<Default><b>We should warm ourselves up
with a drink before we go.</b></Default>

470
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,200
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

471
00:17:57,569 --> 00:17:59,075
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

472
00:17:59,099 --> 00:18:01,476
<Default><b>I think I accidentally
left something in the bath.</b></Default>

473
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:03,585
<Default><b>I'll go ahead and check
the men's section.</b></Default>

474
00:18:03,609 --> 00:18:05,515
<Default><b>Just wait here.</b></Default>

475
00:18:05,539 --> 00:18:06,516
<Default><b>OK!</b></Default>

476
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:07,940
<Default><b>I'll be waiting.</b></Default>

477
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:14,025
<Default><b>I've come to fetch you.</b></Default>

478
00:18:14,049 --> 00:18:15,259
<Default><b>Oh, dear.</b></Default>

479
00:18:22,589 --> 00:18:23,566
<Default><b>Here you go.</b></Default>

480
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:25,099
<Default><b>Is this it?</b></Default>

481
00:18:29,039 --> 00:18:30,039
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

482
00:18:35,339 --> 00:18:37,696
<Default><b>I guess being
the Water Dragon Miko</b></Default>

483
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:40,565
<Default><b>must be a hard job
for one person.</b></Default>

484
00:18:40,589 --> 00:18:42,285
<Default><b>It certainly is.</b></Default>

485
00:18:42,309 --> 00:18:45,156
<Default><b>Everything you do
is to serve the emperor.</b></Default>

486
00:18:45,180 --> 00:18:48,305
<Default><b>Water Dragon Miko is
a fancy name to have.</b></Default>

487
00:18:48,329 --> 00:18:51,936
<Default><b>But what I would do was
hardly fitting of that title.</b></Default>

488
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:54,146
<Default><b>I was leading armies
or carrying out</b></Default>

489
00:18:54,170 --> 00:18:57,025
<Default><b>death sentences
on criminals.</b></Default>

490
00:18:57,049 --> 00:19:00,025
<Default><b>I can't imagine
that's easy.</b></Default>

491
00:19:00,049 --> 00:19:01,926
<Default><b>They were not
all bad either.</b></Default>

492
00:19:01,950 --> 00:19:03,926
<Default><b>Being a criminal
merely meant you caused</b></Default>

493
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:05,426
<Default><b>a problem for
the emperor.</b></Default>

494
00:19:05,450 --> 00:19:06,850
<Default><b>It's sad really.</b></Default>

495
00:19:09,799 --> 00:19:13,495
<Default><b>Sounds like you were
doing his dirty work.</b></Default>

496
00:19:13,519 --> 00:19:17,906
<Default><b>Even now, I'm sure another
member of my clan is doing it.</b></Default>

497
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:19,956
<Default><b>It's sobering
to think about it all.</b></Default>

498
00:19:19,980 --> 00:19:21,845
<Default><b>You mentioned
your clan before.</b></Default>

499
00:19:21,869 --> 00:19:23,755
<Default><b>But what do you
mean by that?</b></Default>

500
00:19:23,779 --> 00:19:26,735
<Default><b>You see, because of
our fighting prowess</b></Default>

501
00:19:26,759 --> 00:19:29,456
<Default><b>our race always
gets chosen.</b></Default>

502
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:33,505
<Default><b>It's gotten to the point we're
called the slaughter Miko.</b></Default>

503
00:19:33,529 --> 00:19:35,845
<Default><b>What a terrible
nickname.</b></Default>

504
00:19:35,869 --> 00:19:37,476
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Scary, isn't it?</b></Default>

505
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:39,876
<Default><b>I'm actually
pretty spooky.</b></Default>

506
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:41,396
<Default><b>Boy, do I know it.</b></Default>

507
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:42,726
<Default><b>Oh?</b></Default>

508
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:45,775
<Default><b>You were only following
orders back then.</b></Default>

509
00:19:45,799 --> 00:19:47,106
<Default><b>And given your position</b></Default>

510
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:49,676
<Default><b>it's not like you had
much of a choice.</b></Default>

511
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:52,886
<Default><b>It's rare to see the two
of you together like this.</b></Default>

512
00:19:52,910 --> 00:19:56,285
<Default><b>Naofumi was being sweet</b></Default>

513
00:19:56,309 --> 00:19:58,226
<Default><b>You were being nice?</b></Default>

514
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,740
<Default><b>Yeah, maybe I was.</b></Default>

515
00:20:01,579 --> 00:20:03,335
<Default><b>We've got a busy
day tomorrow.</b></Default>

516
00:20:03,359 --> 00:20:04,686
<Default><b>Let's head to bed early.</b></Default>

517
00:20:04,710 --> 00:20:06,110
<Default><b>[BOTH WOMEN] OK.</b></Default>

518
00:20:09,670 --> 00:20:13,075
<Default><b>[suspenseful music]</b></Default>

519
00:20:13,099 --> 00:20:20,099
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

520
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:31,480
<Default><b>Message!</b></Default>

521
00:20:32,539 --> 00:20:35,716
<Default><b>Last night, a town to our rear
suffered a surprise attack</b></Default>

522
00:20:35,740 --> 00:20:37,416
<Default><b>by the government army.</b></Default>

523
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,636
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

524
00:20:38,660 --> 00:20:40,095
<Default><b>This is bad.</b></Default>

525
00:20:40,119 --> 00:20:42,666
<Default><b>We left Itsuki and Rishia
in the town behind us.</b></Default>

526
00:20:42,690 --> 00:20:47,095
<Default><b>Atla, Sane, and Fohl, can
you take Gaelion and go help?</b></Default>

527
00:20:47,119 --> 00:20:49,095
<Default><b>- We're on it!
- Leave it to us.</b></Default>

528
00:20:49,119 --> 00:20:55,075
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

529
00:20:55,099 --> 00:20:57,035
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

530
00:20:57,059 --> 00:20:58,126
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

531
00:20:58,150 --> 00:20:59,235
<Default><b>Look at this!</b></Default>

532
00:20:59,259 --> 00:21:00,636
<Default><b>What is going on?</b></Default>

533
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:01,946
<Default><b>Reporting!</b></Default>

534
00:21:01,970 --> 00:21:03,815
<Default><b>We have a message
from someone claiming</b></Default>

535
00:21:03,839 --> 00:21:05,535
<Default><b>to be an enemy
messenger.</b></Default>

536
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:07,055
<Default><b>From the enemy?</b></Default>

537
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:11,406
<Default><b>To the commanding
rebel leader from the...</b></Default>

538
00:21:11,430 --> 00:21:12,995
<Default><b>Water Dragon Miko.</b></Default>

539
00:21:13,019 --> 00:21:14,825
<Default><b>The Water Dragon Miko?</b></Default>

540
00:21:14,849 --> 00:21:16,176
<Default><b>[MAN] What's it say?</b></Default>

541
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,896
<Default><b>Read it aloud, please.</b></Default>

542
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,335
<Default><b>[MAN] Yes, ma'am.</b></Default>

543
00:21:19,359 --> 00:21:22,065
<Default><b>Last night, one of my units
took rash action.</b></Default>

544
00:21:22,089 --> 00:21:23,825
<Default><b>This was not my wish
as commander</b></Default>

545
00:21:23,849 --> 00:21:25,156
<Default><b>of the government army.</b></Default>

546
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:27,035
<Default><b>I have regained
control of them.</b></Default>

547
00:21:27,059 --> 00:21:28,985
<Default><b>For this war</b></Default>

548
00:21:29,009 --> 00:21:30,966
<Default><b>representatives
of both sides meet</b></Default>

549
00:21:30,990 --> 00:21:32,976
<Default><b>and try to
talk things out.</b></Default>

550
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,755
<Default><b>I will represent
our army.</b></Default>

551
00:21:34,779 --> 00:21:36,275
<Default><b>And I would have
your commander</b></Default>

552
00:21:36,299 --> 00:21:38,176
<Default><b>or someone
of equivalent standing</b></Default>

553
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:40,116
<Default><b>represent your side.</b></Default>

554
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:42,156
<Default><b>That's a rather
one-sided ask.</b></Default>

555
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:44,186
<Default><b>Well, for my family</b></Default>

556
00:21:44,210 --> 00:21:45,696
<Default><b>shockingly considerate.</b></Default>

557
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,446
<Default><b>Let me see that letter
for myself.</b></Default>

558
00:21:47,470 --> 00:21:48,466
<Default><b>Yes, sir.</b></Default>

559
00:21:48,490 --> 00:21:55,450
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

560
00:22:04,950 --> 00:22:06,295
<Default><b>[theme music]</b></Default>

561
00:22:06,319 --> 00:22:07,555
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

562
00:22:07,579 --> 00:22:09,049
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

563
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:39,000
<Default><b>PRAYER</b></Default>

